[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-19T18:40:11+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/08/FieldsOfMistria_2024-08-23_14-12-48.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">In <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/441962\">Fields of Mistria</a></em>, there are quite a few <strong>romanceable characters </strong>that you can woo by giving gifts to. You\u2019ll run into these characters in your day-to-day and those wanting to rush to that romance will need to know exactly what to give them.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">It should be noted that while there are romance candidates who will speak a bit flirtily to you, <strong>there is currently no dating or marriage in this early access stage of the game</strong>. Romance candidates have special cutscenes that unlock once you reach a certain number of hearts with them,", "id": 1547351, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/fields-of-mistria-guides/443158/romance-marriage-candidates-characters-best-gifts", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Fields of Mistria romance and best gifts list", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-19T17:21:17+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23212847/dark_souls_book.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Sony is looking to purchase <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/news/481294/sony-fromsoftware-kadokawa-acquisition-talks\">Japanese media conglomerate Kadokawa</a>, according to two anonymous sources<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sony-talks-buy-media-powerhouse-behind-elden-ring-sources-say-2024-11-19/\"> who spoke with Reuters</a>. This acquisition could have major implications across industries, as Kadokawa owns publishers in print media, anime, and gaming. It may create stronger international opportunities for tabletop designers impacted by potential U.S. tariffs and the EU\u2019s soon-to-be-implemented <a href=\"https://co", "id": 1547017, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/481764/sony-acquisition-kadokawa-japanese-tabletop-industry-ttrpg", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Sony\u2019s potential purchase of Dark Souls developer may change the Japanese tabletop industry", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-19T17:01:26+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25120950/polygon_world_of_warcraft_classic_permadeath.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The original <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/world-of-warcraft\">World of Warcraft</a></em> was released on Nov. 23, 2004 and, what now feels like overnight, changed the industry forever. A longstanding and deeply embedded player base, plus the game\u2019s innovation in live service and massively multiplayer online gaming, have made<em> World of Warcraft</em> one of the most played video games of all time.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Here, you\u2019ll find a collection of stories about <em>World of Warcraft</em> today, 20 years ago, and at many notable points between (remember the blood plague?).</p>\n", "id": 1547018, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/world-of-warcraft/481722/world-of-warcraft-20th-anniversary", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Remembering 20 years of World of Warcraft", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-19T16:05:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/polygon-mosaic-21.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Connoisseurs of fluffy, <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/pokemon/23543043/pokemon-squishmallow-walmart-target-rerelease\">huggable Pok\u00e9mon</a> can now look forward to a new set of goodies to add to their digital shopping carts. Pok\u00e9mon and the plush brand Squishmallow have returned with two new Pok\u00e9mon in its line: Eevee and Chansey. First announced in early November, these two toys are now up for pre-order online starting on Tuesday. </p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">You can pre-order both the <a href=\"https://www.pokemoncenter.com/category/squishmallows-plush\">Chansey and Eevee versions at The Pok\u00e9mon Center</a> online. The 12-inch version costs $29.99 for ea", "id": 1546597, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pokemon/481600/eevee-chansey-squishmallows-preorder-how", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Eevee and Chansey Squishmallows are now up for pre-order", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-19T15:55:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Graphic: Polygon | Source images: Studio Wildcard; Quantic Dream/Lucasfilm Games; The Initiative, Crystal Dynamics/Xbox Game Studios\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/polygon-mosaic-7.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Over the past decade, <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/events/479292/game-awards-2024-start-time-nominees\">The Game Awards</a> has become a home for major video game reveals. Geoff Keighley\u2019s annual celebration of gaming is arguably as much about the trailers than the actual awards handed out to game developers, streamers, esports athletes, and voice actors every December. Publishers like to make a big splash at The Game Awards, even if the games they\u2019re announcing aren\u2019t expected to be out for years. Hence, big trailers that rarely p", "id": 1546598, "language": null, "link": "https://www.po